## 2. Complete Technology Stack

### 2.1 Core Framework & Runtime

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| **Python** | 3.12 | Core language |
| **FastAPI** | 0.109.0 | REST API framework (async, high-performance) |
| **Uvicorn** | 0.27.0 | ASGI server for serving the FastAPI app |
| **Pydantic** | <2.0 | Data validation, serialization, and type-safe schemas |
| **python-multipart** | 0.0.6 | File upload handling in FastAPI |

### 2.2 PDF Processing

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| **pdfplumber** | 0.11.0 | PDF text extraction — page-by-page text extraction with layout analysis |

### 2.3 NLP & Machine Learning

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| **spaCy** | 3.7.2 | Natural Language Processing — Named Entity Recognition (NER) |
| **en_core_web_trf** | 3.8.0 | spaCy's transformer-based English model (uses RoBERTa under the hood) |
| **Sentence-Transformers** | 2.3.1 | Generates dense vector embeddings for semantic skill matching |
| **all-MiniLM-L6-v2** | — | Lightweight sentence embedding model (384-dim vectors) |
| **FAISS (CPU)** | 1.8.0 | Facebook AI Similarity Search — vector similarity index for skill matching |

### 2.4 Utilities & Infrastructure

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| **python-dotenv** | 1.0.0 | Environment variable management |
| **ReportLab** | 4.4.10 | PDF generation (for test data/reports) |
| **Requests** | latest | HTTP client |
| **NumPy** | (dependency) | Numerical operations for FAISS embeddings |
| **difflib** | (stdlib) | Fuzzy string matching for typo correction |
| **regex (re)** | (stdlib) | Pattern matching for emails, phones, date ranges |

### 2.5 Deployment & Infrastructure

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Hosting** | AWS EC2 instance |
| **Port** | 8001 (separate from main Praktiki backend) |
