## 3. System Architecture

### 3.1 High-Level Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Client Layer"
        FE["Praktiki Frontend<br/>(React)"]
    end

    subgraph "API Layer"
        API["FastAPI Server<br/>Port 8001<br/>Uvicorn ASGI"]
        CORS["CORS Middleware"]
    end

    subgraph "Processing Pipeline"
        PDF["PDF Processor<br/>(pdfplumber)"]
        ENT["Entity Extractor<br/>(spaCy NER)"]
        SKL["Skills Extractor<br/>(FAISS + Sentence-Transformers)"]
        EXP["Experience Extractor<br/>(Regex Patterns)"]
    end

    subgraph "AI/ML Models (Loaded at Startup)"
        ROBERTA["RoBERTa Transformer<br/>(en_core_web_trf)"]
        MINILM["MiniLM-L6-v2<br/>(Sentence Embedding)"]
        FAISS["FAISS Index<br/>(118 skills, 384-dim)"]
    end

    subgraph "Monitoring & Feedback"
        MON["Production Monitor<br/>(In-memory + JSONL logs)"]
        FB["Human Feedback Loop<br/>(POST /feedback)"]
    end

    FE -->|"POST /parse<br/>(PDF Upload)"| CORS
    CORS --> API
    API --> PDF
    PDF -->|"Raw Text"| ENT
    PDF -->|"Raw Text"| SKL
    PDF -->|"Raw Text"| EXP
    ENT --> ROBERTA
    SKL --> MINILM
    SKL --> FAISS
    API --> MON
    FE -->|"POST /feedback"| FB
    FB --> MON
```

### 3.2 Request Flow (Data Pipeline)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Server
    participant PDF as PDF Processor
    participant NER as Entity Extractor
    participant Skills as Skills Extractor
    participant Exp as Experience Extractor
    participant Mon as Production Monitor

    Client->>API: POST /parse (PDF file)
    API->>API: Validate file (size, extension)
    API->>PDF: extract_text_from_bytes(file_content)
    PDF-->>API: raw_text (string)
    
    par Parallel Extraction
        API->>NER: extract_all_entities(text)
        NER->>NER: spaCy NER → PERSON entities
        NER->>NER: Regex → email pattern
        NER->>NER: Regex → phone pattern
        NER-->>API: (name, email, phone)
    and
        API->>Skills: extract_skills(text)
        Skills->>Skills: Step 1: Exact matching
        Skills->>Skills: Step 2: Alias resolution
        Skills->>Skills: Step 3: Fuzzy matching (difflib)
        Skills->>Skills: Step 4: Semantic FAISS search
        Skills-->>API: skills[]
    and
        API->>Exp: extract_experiences(text)
        Exp->>Exp: Regex → date ranges
        Exp->>Exp: Context extraction
        Exp-->>API: experiences[]
    end
    
    API->>API: Build ResumeData object
    API->>Mon: log_parse_result()
    API-->>Client: ParseResponse (JSON)
```

