## 7. Configuration & Tuning

All configurable parameters are centralized in [config.py](file:///c:/Users/karti/computer_science/praktiki/PythonProject/resume_parser/config.py):

| Parameter | Value | Description |
|-----------|-------|-------------|
| `SPACY_MODEL` | `en_core_web_trf` | spaCy model for NER |
| `SENTENCE_TRANSFORMER_MODEL` | `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` | Embedding model |
| `FAISS_INDEX_DIM` | 384 | Embedding vector dimension |
| `FAISS_SIMILARITY_THRESHOLD` | 0.75 | Min cosine similarity for semantic skill match |
| `MAX_FILE_SIZE_MB` | 10 | Maximum PDF upload size |
| `ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS` | `{".pdf"}` | Accepted file types |
| `MIN_NAME_WORDS` | 2 | Minimum words to consider as a person's name |
| `MAX_NAME_WORDS` | 4 | Maximum words in a person's name |
| `SKILL_LIST` | 118 skills | Master list of canonical skills |
| `SKILL_ALIASES` | 68 aliases | Alias → canonical mapping |
| `SKILL_ONTOLOGY` | 20+ entries | Hierarchical skill relationships |

